Walk like a man

01:39:06.736 --> 01:39:08.670
- Bye-aye, baby
- Ooh-wa-ooh

01:39:08.738 --> 01:39:10.865
- I don't mean maybe
- Ooh-wa-ooh

01:39:10.941 --> 01:39:14.877
- Gonna get along somehow
- Ooh-wa-ooh-wa, ooh-wa-ooh

01:39:14.945 --> 01:39:16.879
- Soon you'll be cryin'
- Ooh-wa-ooh

01:39:16.947 --> 01:39:18.881
- On account of all your lyin'
- Ooh-wa-ooh

01:39:18.949 --> 01:39:21.417
Oh, yeah
just look who's laughing now

01:39:21.484 --> 01:39:24.942
I'm gonna walk like a man

01:39:25.021 --> 01:39:26.955
Fast as I can

01:39:27.023 --> 01:39:30.982
Walk like a man
from you

01:39:31.061 --> 01:39:34.997
I'll tell the world
forget about it, girl

01:39:35.065 --> 01:39:39.559
And walk like a man
from you

01:39:39.636 --> 01:39:41.763
Oooh

01:39:48.745 --> 01:39:51.680
Mmmm

01:39:55.785 --> 01:40:00.552
The years
they come and go

01:40:02.959 --> 01:40:07.623
And change will come
I know

01:40:09.366 --> 01:40:12.699
You won't

01:40:12.769 --> 01:40:16.466
Be there

01:40:16.539 --> 01:40:20.031
My heart

01:40:20.110 --> 01:40:24.547
And soul

01:40:24.614 --> 01:40:29.313
Different time and place

01:40:31.621 --> 01:40:37.287
But time cannot erase

01:40:38.662 --> 01:40:43.656
The smile
that lights your face

01:40:45.368 --> 01:40:49.031
As you gaze in mine

01:40:49.105 --> 01:40:52.370
It will always shine

01:40:52.442 --> 01:40:56.538
And you

01:40:56.613 --> 01:41:00.208
Will always be

01:41:00.283 --> 01:41:03.616
An angel making sure I care

01:41:03.687 --> 01:41:07.248
A memory that's always there

01:41:07.324 --> 01:41:14.025
You dreams won't die
They live inside of me

01:41:14.097 --> 01:41:18.056
You know you'll always be

01:41:18.134 --> 01:41:24.664
My heart and soul

01:41:24.741 --> 01:41:28.074
Oooh

